values:
Boring, boring, boring, boooo~ring.

I really hope something interesting happens in the next few days.

You owe me, Ron. You too Hermione ^_^

Now, now, I saw this set to make jokes in the mall and I would love to have it, you know~

Ah, how pleasnt feels so great to win.

We're totally going to that masquerade, right Fred? I need to keep an eye on a certain bet I made ^_^

[[Strikes, icon and mood viewable only to Fred]]

Glad that was over.

Not that it wasn't fun but I prefer us being all twin-like, you know~

[Private]

Help me with little Ronniekins here, please?

;~~~~~~~~~~~;

i dun feel ok! tummy aches!!! *whine* ;~~~~;


*sobs*

Freeeed, maek  it go away ;~~~~;

oowwwiee, i tink i ate too much candyyyy x3!! eh heh!

but they were liek real nice!! no wonder why daddy loves muggles so much!! they have the bestest candies!! :DDDD

Fred, u ar the bestest broter evah!!

i still dunno wer i am, but if freds here too then its okay :)

F, F, Fred??? ;~~~~~~~~;

I, I tol yu to not to run so fast!! now I tripped and fell in a rally weir place!! and i kep runnin to find yu but i cant!!!

;~~~~~~~~~~~~~;!!!!

FREEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEED!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!

[[About 5 years old]]

Heh, well that wasn't that bad (in fact quite nice)

Though it was rather strange to sleep in the same bed as Fred... but in the end everything turned out alright :D

Little Dray is in our dorm too. Hiding from muggles! The poor thing Better watch out! I think I heard them walking outside the dorm last night >.>

And Ron now is here too!! I missed teasing him~!

[Private]

Of course, that doesn't means I don't want him to be his normal age already.

But at least he's cute and doesn't drive me insane~

[[First strike legible only to Draco. Second strike totally legible]]

Sweet Merlin, there are too many midgets around...

... Fred? Where did you go bro?

Ow.

That's it. That was the last time I tried doing that, Fred.

Ow, just ow.

Fred? Where the hell are you dear brother? I thought you wanted me to make it up for the other day~

And with this fire thing going around you better be okay.

[[Strike Legible only to Fred]]

Dear lovely Mello:

As much as I enjoyed being with you all day today even bathing ;D I'm afraid I definitely don't plan to sleep next to you. 

The reason? Simple, I won't be able to sleep at all ^_^

So yeah, come here already so I'll be able to kiss you ;D

[[Strike Legible xD He could be just joking... or not... xD it's all up to Mello!mun :3]]

So, going along with the masses, I'm stuck with a blode guy apparently Matt's boyfriend 

Wonder how now, this place is pretty unusual Though now that I think about it, I can take advantage of this situations *smirk*

I'm sorry I'll have to cheat on you, Fred~

[[First strike Legible, second Strike Illegible. Mood is hidden]]

Oooh, a party~! Looks like it's gonna be such an interesting event!

[Filtered to Fred]

And a perfect opportunity to test some things.

What do you say Gred?

[[Mood and icon visible only to Fred. Other people see the default icon and 'cheerful' in mood]]

Some people are so touchy. Too bad.

Good thing that it's finally done.

But now I'm kinda bored. What to do? What to do~?

[[Mood and Icon visible only to Fred. The rest see 'bored' and the default icon]]

Dear brother.

Are you up to no good~? ;D

Aw, the amusement park is gone already??

What a shame, just when we figured out how to make that cotton candy machine explode successfully.

Oh, and to the people whose dorms are next to us... don't mind the explosions, 'kay? ;D

Don't believe to whatever the lady in charge of the cotton machine says~!

We didn't do it!!! XDDDDDDDD

[[They kinda made the machine go crazy and started to make tons and TONS of cotton candy (ya know, like a REALLY big ball of it XD;) *snort* Don't ask how XD;]]

It's certainly fun seeing little Malfoy spinning around in those rides! *snort*  

Hey, feeling like throwing up already?

Aniusebent  Amusement Park, huh?

Muggles are really fun and interesting. 

Guess we're gonna go to see how it is.

Let's see... I might do a list of what spells I can do succesfully without fainting or anything.

-Lumos
-Point Me
-Sonorus
-Quietus
-Nox


Spells that work but not so succesfully:

-Wingardium Leviosa
-Accio
-Aguamenti
-Avis
-Engorgio
-Reparo
-Protego
-Reducio
-Reducto
-Mobili
-Scourgify
-Silencio
-Tergeo
-Locomotor
-Incendio
-Evanesco
-Oppugno
-And some jinxes~

That's all for now, all the others made my head hurt~

Pfft, is that all you had Hikaru? Just a spicy ball and a sticky something :P

Baah, nothing that the great George Weasley couldn't handle~ And thank God I still have some Licorice Wands.

Now I miss Quidditch and this is all your fault Ginny~

[[Strike Illegible]]

This place isn't as bad as I though~ It has some really interesting stuff. 

Uniforms aren't that bad anymore~ They just needed some useful changes. 

I needed to make a list of the things I had when I got here: 

~My robe, of course (at least it's my favourite) 
~Underwear (not my favourite but at least it was a clean pair XD) 
~My wand (Though I only can do simple spells) 
~Some money (9 Galleons, 11 sickles and 17 knuts to be exact) (I wonder if we could exchange them from 'Avorian money'..) 
~A couple of Licorice Wands. 
~Some Bertie Botts. 
~The list of what I was supossed to going to buy before I started looking for Fred. 

That's all. 

Oh, and I don't like my bed~. Do something about it.

Let's see how it is Avoria so far...

Dorms are ok (sharing a dorm with Fred, as always <3), beds are ok, almost as good as the Hogwarts ones but not as good as the one we bought (damn I miss our bed).

Oooh, and it has an interesting muggle kitchen! A place that should never mix up with us (I mean, if we even managed to make explode mother's kitchen...).

We have to go to school, it's a bit annoying since we escaped from our last school, but being a muggle school promises to be a little interesting at least so we'll give it a try ;D (after all, Professor Lupin and Professor Snape would be there *snort*)

Uniforms are stupid (they made me feel like a good person) Green doesn't suits you Fred.

The fact that I can't apparate sucks~

And for the people who doesn't knows:

'You-Know-Who' is an evil wizard from our world with a terrifying power~ Oh, and he eat babies.

If after this you're still asking about it, it'll mean that you're, indeed, stupid.

[EDIT]

And for the record.

Muggle= Non Magical Person (AKA.- People who can't use magic) = Not an insult.

kthnksbai.

Okaaaaaay, I must say, Fred, that this is certainly NOT funny.

First you hide somewhere making me actually worry about you (do you have any idea for how long I'd been looking for you?) , and then you hide a port key on that boxes and now I found myself in a rather weird place. Oh, and you even paid to that woman so she'll start babbling about alternate universes. Original, I must admit.

Haha, how funny, see I'm laughing?

Now you better show your lame ass up right now before I start getting hysteric.

....


Because this is a joke.... right?

[[Strike Legible to Fred xD; I need pics DX I'm going to put some as soon as I get home]]
